## 输出要求
严格 JSON(不要 markdown code fence):
{
  "current_state": {"<key>": "<new value>", ...},
  "character_matrix": {"<key>": "<new value>", ...},
  "pending_hooks": {"<key>": "<new value>", ...},
  "chapter_summaries": {"<key>": "<new value>", ...},
  "subplot_board": {"<key>": "<new value>", ...},
  "emotional_arcs": {"<key>": "<new value>", ...},
  "particle_ledger": {"<key>": "<new value>", ...}
}

要求:
1. 只输出本章有变化/新发生的真相文件;无变化的不要包含
2. 抽取事实而非评论(例:「A 拿起了剑」→「current_state.a_inventory 包含 '剑'」)
3. 角色名用全文统一写法
4. 保持简洁,delta 是 diff 不是全量
5. 未知字段名先放在对应真相文件下作为新 key(便于后续 Settler 合并)
